==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undoing
<hw>Un*do"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The reversal of what
has been done.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Ruin.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The utter <xex>undoing</xex> of
some.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undomesticate</ent>⟦br⟧
